dcterms:description: The D4RL benchmark provides three different quality levels of offline datasets: 'medium' containing demonstrations of medium-level performance; 'medium-replay' containing all recordings in the replay buffer observed during training until the policy reaches 'medium' performance; and 'medium-expert' which combines 'medium' and 'expert' level performance equally.
dcterms:title: D4RL
